OL,3,CYoga teacher aims to raise awareness
OL,4,Cof origins and meaning of the practice
OL,6,FA yoga teacher is trying to raise
OL,7,Fawareness of the discipline's origins
OL,8,Fand the meaning behind the practice.
OL,10,FChandni Nijhawan teaches in
OL,11,FPetersfield, Hampshire with a
OL,12,Fspiritual and holistic approach -
OL,13,Falongside the physical postures.
OL,15,FYoga was discovered by ancient sages
OL,16,Fin India, believed to be around 5,000
OL,17,Fyears ago, but it is also evident in
OL,18,Fsome of the earliest texts in the
OL,19,FHindu religion.
