OL,3,CYoga teacher aims to raise awareness
OL,4,Cof origins and meaning of the practice
OL,6,F"I'm Eastern as I grew up and I'm
OL,7,FWestern in my education and my living.
OL,8,FExpanding the world of yoga, that's my
OL,9,Fdream.
OL,11,F"Yoga is more than just a posture that
OL,12,Fwe see on Instagram, like a handstand
OL,13,F- I'm not saying that's not yoga, but
OL,14,Fit's just a snippet."
OL,16,FIn recent years, yoga has seen a boom
OL,17,Fin popularity, with millions taking
OL,18,Fpart across the world.
