OL,3,CYoga teacher aims to raise awareness
OL,4,Cof origins and meaning of the practice
OL,6,FAlong with it, many different trends
OL,7,Fhave popped up, including classes with
OL,8,Fanimals, dance music, and even alcohol.
OL,10,FA social media creator on TikTok,
OL,11,Fhowever, wants to remind people of the
OL,12,Fimportance of a minimalistic practice.
OL,14,FYoga teacher and social media creator,
OL,15,FNikita Desai said: "The practice
OL,16,Fintends for us to turn inwards and
OL,17,Flook within ourselves so we're trying
OL,18,Fto navigate ourselves away from
OL,19,Fexternal distractions.
